OL,7,FUnder the new age ratings, classic
OL,8,Ffilms including Goldfinger and From
OL,9,FRussia With Love could be reclassified
OL,10,Ffrom PG to 12A, ITV News Correspondent
OL,11,FLucy Watson reports
OL,13,FThe British Board of Film
OL,14,FClassification (BBFC) has released new
OL,15,Fclassification guidelines for the
OL,16,Ffirst time in five years.
OL,18,FThe updated guidelines, which are
OL,19,Freviewed every five years, reflect
OL,20,Fshifts in public opinion and changing
OL,21,Fvalues of people across the UK.
