OL,5,Cratings
OL,7,FViolent on-screen action and sex
OL,8,Fscenes are likely to be classified
OL,9,Fwith higher age ratings.
OL,11,FThe BBFC spoke to 12,000 people across
OL,12,Fthe UK as part of the consultation
OL,13,Finto the changes.
OL,15,FWhat has changed?
OL,17,FThe classification age brackets will
OL,18,Fremain the same as before, going from
OL,19,Fa U all the way to 18.
