OL,7,FSince the BBFC last carried out
OL,8,Fresearch in 2019 depictions of suicide
OL,9,Fand self-harm rose to the second
OL,10,Fbiggest area of concern, with
OL,11,Frespondents saying they wanted to be
OL,12,Fwarned about this type of content.
OL,14,FRespondents also said they wanted a
OL,15,Fmore cautious approach to classifying
OL,16,Fsex scenes at 12A.
