OL,4,Cviolence and sex under tighter new age
OL,5,Cratings
OL,7,FSince 2019, audiences have become more
OL,8,Frelaxed about cannabis use and solvent
OL,9,Fmisuse.
OL,11,FThe research revealed people are now
OL,12,Fmore accepting of incidental cannabis
OL,13,Fmisuse at 12A/12, so long as it is not
OL,14,Fdetailed, glamorised or frequent.
OL,16,FIn future, the BBFC will says it will
OL,17,Ftake a less restrictive approach to
OL,18,Fsuch content.
