OL,7,FUnder the new age ratings, classic
OL,8,Ffilms including Goldfinger and From
OL,9,FRussia With Love could be reclassified
OL,10,Ffrom PG (Parental Guidance) to 12A to
OL,11,Freflect updated values.
OL,13,FThe Mitchells Vs the Machines (2021)
OL,14,Fwas originally rated a U for mild
OL,15,Fviolence, very mild threat, rude
OL,16,Fhumour, and language. This may now be
OL,17,Fchanged to a PG as focus groups said
OL,18,Fthe violence was too intense and scary
OL,19,Ffor very young viewers.
