OL,8,Fwould have previously been categorised
OL,9,Fas a 15 under the previous BBFC
OL,10,Fguidelines, but under the new
OL,11,Fclassifications would become a 12A.
OL,13,FThis is because of the specific
OL,14,Fcultural and historic context of
OL,15,Fcannabis use in Jamaica in the 1960s
OL,16,Fand 70s. There is also a strong anti-
OL,17,Fviolence message in the film
